document_data.name: Domgarten
document_data.mainbody: '''Domgarten''' was a young [[elf]] scout during the late 15th century [[DR]].
document_data.History: Domgarten was one of the elf scouts of the [[Moonwood]] during the [[War of the Silver Marches]] of [[1484 DR]]â€“[[1485 DR]]. He went with the top scout [[Myriel]] to inspect the ground of a battle between [[dwarves]] and [[orcs]].
